<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'self'; img-src 'self' https: data:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; script-src 'self'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self';" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-Frame-Options" content="DENY" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-Content-Type-Options" content="nosniff" />
  <meta http-equiv="Referrer-Policy" content="no-referrer" />
  <meta http-equiv="Strict-Transport-Security" content="max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ruan Pororoca | Surf na Pororoca</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #0b1f1a;
      color: #eafaf5;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)), url('onda-pororoca.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    header p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    section {
      padding: 80px 10%;
    }

    .sobre {
      background: #0f2e25;
    }

    .sobre h2,
    .galeria h2,
    .contato h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #7fffd4;
    }

    .sobre p {
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .galeria {
      background: #081613;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .grid img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }

    .grid img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .contato {
      background: #0f2e25;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .contato a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background: #7fffd4;
      color: #0b1f1a;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contato a:hover {
      background: #5fd6b3;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #050d0b;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!--
    ⚠️ Aviso de Segurança
    Este site é monitorado.
    Tentativas de exploração, injeção de código ou uso indevido
    podem ser registradas.
  -->

  <script>
    (function () {
      try {
        console.log(
          "%cAcesso indevido é monitorado.",
          "color:red;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;"
        );
      } catch (e) {}
    })();
  </script>

  <header>
    <h1>RUAN POROROCA</h1>
    <p>Surfando a força da natureza. A pororoca como estilo de vida.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="sobre">
    <h2>Sobre</h2>
    <p>
      Ruan Pororoca é surfista da Baixada Maranhense, referência no surf de pororoca no Rio Mearim.
      Conectado com o rio, a maré e a floresta, transforma um fenômeno natural em expressão,
      resistência e cultura.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="galeria">
    <h2>Ondas da Pororoca</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <img src="onda1.jpg" alt="Pororoca 1">
      <img src="onda2.jpg" alt="Pororoca 2">
      <img src="onda3.jpg" alt="Pororoca 3">
      <img src="onda4.jpg" alt="Pororoca 4">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contato">
    <h2>Contato</h2>
    <p>Expedições, parcerias e projetos.</p>
    <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 — Ruan Pororoca • Surf & Natureza
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
